
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head'); %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="public/css/stylehome.css">
</head>
<body class="container">
    <header>
        <%- include('../partials/header'); %>
    </header>
    <main>
  

        <figure class= "hero">
            <img src="public/images/homepageimage1.jpeg" alt="image" width="100%" height="auto">
        </figure>
        <div class="contain">
            <div class="product-content">
                <ul class="container-left-panel">
                    <% products.forEach(function(product){ %>
                        <li>
                            <div>
                                <h6><%= product.productName %></h6>
                                <p><%= product.category %></p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    <% }); %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        
            <div class= "home-content">
                <div class="item1">
                    <p class = "para">We are a new generation balloon supplier where you can buy direct from the 
                    wholesaler at wholesale pricing. We are United states's first and exclusive Sempertex 
                    distributor, the highest quality balloon manufacturer in the world. We strive to
                    keep all costs down by eliminating our walk-in services, allowing us to focus 
                    completely on our website and ordering platform, to serve you better! You can feel 
                    safe and comfortable that our experienced team will be able to help you in any request 
                    that you may have. Our goal is to provide the most advanced balloon navigation and ordering 
                    platform with lowest possible balloon prices</p>
                    
                
                    <p class = "para">Our wide selection offers different styles of balloons to fit everyone’s needs 
                    from single balloons to packaged balloon bouquets as well as anything required to
                    transform a room with beautiful balloon decor. We are glad that you chose Balloonatic Asylum 
                    to liven up your party! We carry many of the world’s finest balloon manufactures such as Anagram, 
                    Sempertex, Convergram, Hi-Float and many more.</p>

                </div>

            

                <aside class= "item2">
                    <h4>Customer Tributes</h4>
                    <p class = "quote" id="quotes"><%=qoutes.qoute %></p>
                    <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
                    <script>
                        setInterval(function() {                            
                            $.ajax({
                              "url":"localhost:9090/getqoutes",
                              "success":function(data){
                                 $("#quotes").innerHTML(data.qoute);
                              },
                              "error":function(error){
                              //handle error here
                              }
                           })
                        }, 30000)
                       </script>
                </aside>

            </div>
    </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <%- include('../partials/footer'); %>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>